### Change 2 — `DiffusionProcessorRegistry.java` — Add HISTORICAL case

```java
public List<ItemProcessor<?, ?>> resolveProcessors(DiffusionStepContextI context) {
    return switch (context.providerIndexProcess()) {
        case STATIC_INDEX, PRICES_INDEX -> List.of(
                new NotRequiredSecurityFilter(context),
                new UndiffusedScopeFilter(context, elasticsearchService),
                new TickerUpdater(context),
                new ProviderDataEnricher(context, providerDataFetcher, outputMapper));

        case DERIVED_INDEX -> List.of(
                new NotRequiredSecurityFilter(context),
                new UndiffusedScopeFilter(context, elasticsearchService),
                new ProviderDataEnricher(context, providerDataFetcher, outputMapper));

        // Process H: same chain as DERIVED — no TickerUpdater needed for historical data
        case HISTORICAL -> List.of(
                new NotRequiredSecurityFilter(context),
                new UndiffusedScopeFilter(context, elasticsearchService),
                new ProviderDataEnricher(context, providerDataFetcher, outputMapper));

        default -> throw new IllegalArgumentException(
                "Unknown diffusedData: " + context.diffusedData());
    };
}
```

